OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave should cover
OL,4,Cmiscarriage, say MPs
OL,6,FSince April 2020 employees can be
OL,7,Feligible for statutory parental
OL,8,Fbereavement leave and pay if there is
OL,9,Fa stillbirth after 24 weeks of
OL,10,Fpregnancy, but there is no specific
OL,11,Fleave for a pre-24 week loss in the
OL,12,Fform of miscarriage.
OL,14,FThe committee said the two-week leave
OL,15,Fperiod should be also made available
OL,16,Fto those bereaved as a result of pre-
OL,17,F24 week pregnancy loss.
