OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave should cover
OL,4,Cmiscarriage, say MPs
OL,6,FThe committee said an estimated more
OL,7,Fthan one in five pregnancies end
OL,8,Fbefore 24 weeks, with between 10% and
OL,9,F20% of pregnancies ending in the first
OL,10,F12 weeks, known as early miscarriage.
OL,12,FWhile MPs acknowledged that a "growing
OL,13,Fnumber of employers have specific
OL,14,Fpregnancy loss leave and pay
OL,15,Fpolicies", such as NHS Trusts and the
OL,16,FCo-op, they said there remain "very
OL,17,Fsubstantial gaps in provision".
