OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave should cover
OL,4,Cmiscarriage, say MPs
OL,6,FTaking evidence, the committee heard
OL,7,Fthat sick pay is too little for many
OL,8,Fwomen and their partners to be able to
OL,9,Fafford to take the time off they need,
OL,10,Fwhile it also does not offer the
OL,11,Fconfidentiality many women want, with
OL,12,Femployees often required to report the
OL,13,Freason for their absence directly to
OL,14,Ftheir line manager.
OL,16,FCommittee chairwoman Sarah Owen has
OL,17,Fpreviously spoken of her own loss,
OL,18,Fsaying she was "not prepared for the
OL,19,Fgrief of miscarrying".
