OL,3,CPaid bereavement leave should cover
OL,4,Cmiscarriage, say MPs
OL,6,F"The committee's report found many
OL,7,Fprivate sector employers, plus the
OL,8,FNHS, the largest public sector
OL,9,Femployer of women, are successfully
OL,10,Foffering paid bereavement leave for
OL,11,Fthose who miscarry, but provision is
OL,12,Fnot universal.
OL,14,F"The case for a minimum standard in
OL,15,Flaw is overwhelming. A period of paid
OL,16,Fleave should be available to all women
OL,17,Fand partners who experience a pre-24-
OL,18,Fweek pregnancy loss. It's time to
OL,19,Finclude bereavement leave for workers
OL,20,Fwho miscarry in new employment rights
OL,21,Flaws."
